reviewText: Our whole family loves his cd's.  The words to the songs are very moving.  Love messianic type of cd's This and Lamb are our utmost favorites.

I recomment this...  great music...  great spirit...

Fills this temple...  sweet !!!

The secret..you don't sing about God you sing TO God!!!!!  This is what is so special about Messianic praise and worship.  I've been listening to Christian music since 1978 but after hearing this music I find it rather lacking.

Paul Wilbur has done an excellent job with this concert.  The worship definitely magnifies the spirit of the Lord
If you are seeking a video to watch and worship with, then this is the one.

Wonderful video recorded live in Jerusalem, Paul Wilbur takes you to the presence of God singing songs that come from His Throne. You'll feel like you're in heaven, simply the best video I've ever known.

This is an excellent live worship presentation by Paul Wilbur. I wish I could have been in the audience when this performance was taped. Our grandchildren were very "spell bound" when they watched it with us. We watch this DVD regularly -- it is a very magnificant praise and worship music performance. We purchased several of Paul Wilbur's products, which are all very excellent. However, this one has been our favorite so far.  I highly recommend it and would give the DVD a 5+ star rating.
We had this on VHS and when I saw it was now on DVD at a fantastic price we immediately purchased it.  It is a great concert that your whole family should enjoy.

This is a killer video. I wish I could have been there in person to experience this. I'm a Worship musician myself and just love this video. I was excited when I seen it on DVD. I have watched the VHS version at 50 times!! yes it's that good, in fact I am going to buy Paul Wilbers other DVD's offered as well. I only wish they would have re-mixed it in 5.1 and included footage of everything else that went on in the process of the making of Jerusalem Arise! JESUS is LORD and this DVD expresses it so beautifully.
Cheyenne Allen

music!

This is probably my favorite Paul Wilbur DVD of all time. It was shot during the Feast of Tabernacles and it is so full of true worship and joy in the Lord. I shared this DVD with friends and they loved it so much. Everyone was on their feet praising God!
it has a wonderful blend of faster Messianic music building up and the beautiful, deep worship that would touch anyone's heart.
I love, love, love thins DVD. The CD is awesome as well.
If you love the Lord, you will love this Disc! Awsome performance and music to stir you up and build you up!
This dvd will remind you why it is so important to worship the Lord.  Every time you watch it you feel great.

Great music. Uplifting worship. It made a Great gift. Excellent mail delivery.

A very nice mix of high energy music and soft worshipful songs.  I'm a big Wilbur fan,and have all of his DVD's and CD's.  This one is my favorite.

Not only is the music and orchestration absolutely incredible but the photography is awe inspiring; everything is sooooo well done, unbelievable! We listen to this constantly as it is so spiritually uplifting, I even wake up in the morning with one of the songs running thru' my head, definitely a wonderful way to start the day. Don't hesitate to add this one to your shopping cart, you won't be sorry!!!
We have been wanting this DVD for a year or two now and finally bought it.  We were not disappointed.  It is great to get the high quality that comes from having the DVD to play.

This DVD is an awesome worship video.  Taped in Israel and the whole DVD is excellent.  Buy it if you love Jewish worship and even if you don't think that you do.  All it took was 2 songs to get me hooked and I'm not even Jewish (that I know of).

The Messianic praise concert is fantastic!  Just as one reviewer said, I just love to listen to this over and over. If ever you are feeling a little down or tired, turn your eyes to the Lord by watching this DVD. One good point to this concert is that the praise and worship turns one's eyes to the Lord and not towards me. Also, the mix of songs is great. Paul Wilbur begins with celebration and praise at the beginning. Then the middle songs bring out the holiness of God and finally rising to a celebration of the Lord's coming. Finally, the back-up orchestra and choir was great with some great arrangements. As my title said, the greatest praise concert I have heard.
Beautiful Product!  One little inconvenience, I have a hard time playing it on my laptop.  I also have difficulties playing in certain DVD players.  But overall, I love it!
We love this video , my 2 years old loves to sing to it and when Paul says the Lord he is God she belts it out .
This is a wonderful DVD.  Uplifting and great worship time.
paul wilbur best performance for the glory of God.

This is my absolute favorite live worship music DVD, and I recommend it to anyone interest in hearing Messianic praise and worship. The style is very soothing and always leaves me with a peaceful feeling after I watch it, and it especially helps me if I watch it when feeling unwell or sad. I really like how it sounds holy and calming without being too loud or pop-influenced in the music style, and the singers have excellent harmony. The scenery is also very beautiful, and I like the way the lyrics alternate between English and Hebrew and repeat enough to quickly memorize them. I only wish it was longer than one hour and that there were subtitles included. I highly recommend this DVD as well as any CDs/DVDs by Paul Wilbur.
I will be ordering more of Paul Wilber
DVD is a must have - The Worship songs are amazing. There is no sound like the Jewish sound of Worship Music. Praise God.!
